            "title": "特朗普請求叫停阻止他罷免庫克的裁定 上訴法院有望周日晚做出判決",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"特朗普請求叫停阻止他罷免庫克的裁定 上訴法院有望周日晚做出判決\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/UOhWIJw9kdfBFvudvnwAvA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-09/560e6dd0-90b2-11f0-b68b-2b87a63fe5d9\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">特朗普請求叫停阻止他罷免庫克的裁定 上訴法院有望周日晚做出判決</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
